2021, Section 1105, as last amended by Section 1,
9 Chapter 148, O.S.L. 2025 (47 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section
1105), which relates to evidence of ownership and
10 compliance with federal law; authorizing certain
inspectors to perform certain vehicle inspections;
11 amending 47 O.S. 2021, Section 1105.3, which relates
to necessity of vehicle identification number;
12 including salvage pools as entities having certain
authorization; and providing an effective date.
