7 Service Oklahoma shall not issue a certificate of title for a
8 vehicle which is subject to the provisions of this paragraph without
9 the required documentation from agencies of the United States and
10 evidence of ownership. Upon receipt of an application without the
11 required documentation, Service Oklahoma shall return the
12 application to the applicant with notice that the certificate of
13 title may not be issued without the required documentation. Nothing
14 in this paragraph shall prohibit Service Oklahoma from issuing
15 certificates of title for antique or classic vehicles not driven
16 upon the public streets, roads, or highways, for mini-trucks
