15 shall collect a fee of Three Dollars ($3.00) which shall be in
16 addition to other fees provided by the Oklahoma Vehicle License and
17 Registration Act. The fee, if collected by the licensed operator
18 pursuant to this subsection, shall be retained by the licensed
19 operator.
20 H. The charge for each certificate of title issued, except for
21 junked titles as defined in paragraph 4 of subsection B of this
22 section, shall be Eleven Dollars ($11.00), which charge shall be in
23 addition to any other fees or taxes imposed by law for such vehicle.
24 One Dollar ($1.00) of each such charge shall be deposited in the
ENGR. H. B. NO. 3277 Page 12

1 Okla homa Tax Commission Reimbursement Fund through December 31,
