13 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 47 O.S. 2021, Section 1105.3, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 Section 1105.3. Every vehicle shall have and contain a vehicle
16 identification number, which number shall not be obliterated,
17 erased, mutilated, removed, or missing. This section shall not
18 affect those persons authorized by law to have in their possession a
19 motor vehicle on which the manufacturer's number or numbers have
20 been obliterated, erased, mutilated, removed, or missing. For the
21 purposes of this section, "persons authorized by law" shall include
22 salvage pools authorized to store vehicles for insurance companies
23 which are requiring inspection.
24 SECTION 3. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
